gameRecap.title: Game Recap: 76ers 131, Wizards 126
gameRecap.excerpt: The 76ers defeated the Wizards, 131-126. Joel Embiid dropped a season-high 50 points, along with 13 rebounds and seven assists for the 76ers, with Tyrese Maxey adding 26 points and seven assists in the victory. Jordan Poole tallied 23 points and two assists for the Wizards in the losing effort. The 76ers improve to 13-7 in the regular season, while the Wizards fall to 3-17.
